column1: Hoooly shit! Is this for real!?

This meat! It's so thick! So soft! Damn,
that's good!
Ryuji, cut it out! You're spitting all over me!
Ahaha... I think Yusuke's crying over here.

I don't even want to know what his regular diet
is like if this is enough to make him cry...
Either way, food's delicious.
Hey, let me have some too!

I swear, you are the noisiest cat on the planet. Ask
[1B]S1 to split some with you.
You heard the dude. Too bad. Just gotta make do with the smell.
Don't be such a pig! I'm hungry too, you know!
Is that a cat I hear?

Am I hearing things? I could've sworn I heard a
cat...

Oh, uh, nope! Not a real cat, at least... We were
just practicing our cat sounds!
Oh, come on... You're not fooling anyone.

Sounds to me like he's in the bag of the
gentleman with the glasses. Aw, that's sweet. Are
you going to share?

You and your cat should partake in the finest
beef tongue this restaurant has to offer!

Oops, sorry, sorry. You're right. If you get
thrown out, then no more beef tongue.
By the way, is this your first time having Sendai beef tongue? I should tell you, the oxtail soup's to die for...

Did you know oxtail soup is packed with
collagen? A lot of people seem to think it's good
for your skin...

They say it's not as effective when ingested, but
there's a fair number of reports that suggest
otherwise.

Human cognition can be quite misleading. You
may think you feel a change when none has
occurred. This is the placebo effect and...
Yo, dude... She's just goin' on and on...
Does she even notice us talking right now?

This overwhelming onslaught of pointless info...
We got ourselves a nerd, ladies and gentlemen.
Uh... Sorry about, y'know, the bag thing...

Huh? What? Oh, you mean the cat? Don't worry.
I won't tell the staff or anything.
By the way, are you all students?

I see! So you'll be taking your college entrance
exams soon! Decided on a university yet?

Hmm, I could see a couple of you being in
college, but not you. You've still got an air of
innocence about you.

In which case, you'll be taking your entrance
exams soon, right? Have you decided where
you're going to apply yet?

If I had to guess, I'd say you're in high school,
right? So you'll be taking your college exams
soon. Have you decided where you'll apply?
Oh, forgive me, I haven't even introduced myself. I'm Kuon Ichinose. I work as a researcher over at Toho University.

Hey, you guys should come check out the
campus. It's way up in the mountains, but it's 
a lot of fun. Lots of bears this season, too.

Oh, uh... You know, we kinda got something
goin' on already, so we don't exactly got the
time...

I see, I see. Yes, well, it's important that you do
what you want while you're still young. Allow
me to impart a little treat till next we meet.

Well, then. I've had my fill of beef tongue,
so it's probably best if I get going.
...So, uh, she was weirdly energetic, huh?

Well, thankfully, we avoided getting in
trouble. We should be grateful she didn't
tell on us.
Nah, I got carried away, too...

Sorry, Mona-chan. We'll buy you some
sasa-kamaboko later.

You mean the fish cake on the skewers with that
nice layer of char on top!? Ooh, I can't wait!

Oh, his latest work was just perfect. I was up
all night reading it. Two nights in a row, if you
can believe that!

Speaking of which, I read in a magazine
interview that he's going to be at the station 
today... There's no way I'm missing that!

All right, let's finish eating. And quietly this
time.
